          "name": "Tempura Matsui",
          "image": "https://media.timeout.com/images/102900123/630/472/image.jpg",
          "cuisine": "Japanese",
          "cost": 3,
          "description": "In the überindulgent world of three-figure omakase thrills, sushi reigns, with finance whales and deep-pocketed diners kneeling at the throne of trumped-up toro. But tempura, Japan’s battered-and-fried preparation of seafood and vegetables, was never a part of that fine-dining fawning. Enter Masao Matsui. ",
